{"tid":933142,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗龍津難食咗好多","createTime":"2018-12-08T10:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T13:21:40.000Z","uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e2be9fc58a90ca25bde2c0f363cd71f632cea65e","tid":933142,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"以前出深水埗站D2出口 都一定會買返塊格仔餅或者雞蛋仔 <br />\n<br />\n嗰度啲格仔餅堪稱全香港最好食 塊餅夠脆又夠厚 食一啖真係咩嘢煩惱都冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雞蛋仔蛋味夠濃亦都好脆<br />\n<br />\n最近行過買咗塊格仔餅 屌你塊格仔餅又薄又淋好撚難食 好似外行人整咁<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋仔都好難食見到啲色水都無胃口<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QETV60f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQETV60f.png&h=c0ab5910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唔想再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28768fd821094537e3836ac3620d38b339701869","tid":933142,"uid":14216,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"嗰度啲格仔餅堪稱全香港最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你食開屎？"},{"pid":"994dc81eb2b9b0abbafdcf5a8280a0b27ad34f63","tid":933142,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"28768fd821094537e3836ac3620d38b339701869","tid":933142,"uid":14216,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"嗰度啲格仔餅堪稱全香港最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你食開屎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"有咩好建議？"},{"pid":"e81b2da9352d7a5226ae62cbabcca95ca8a7619a","tid":933142,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994dc81eb2b9b0abbafdcf5a8280a0b27ad34f63","tid":